## CHARGE AT CLOSING

Note: I._M., D._M., and P._C._W. descend from the dais, and
   all Officers and Companions join them on the level,
   as in the Master Mason Degree.

IM: (_Uncovers head._) Companions, being about to rise up
   from this sacred retreat, to mix again with the world, let
   us not forget, amid the cares and vicissitudes of active
   life, the bright example of sincere friendship, so
   beautifully illustrated in the lives of the founders of this
   degree. Let us take the lesson home with us, and may it
   strengthen the bonds of fraternal love between us, incite
   our hearts to duty, and our desires to wisdom. Let us
   exercise Charity, cherish Hope, walk in Faith, and may
   that moral principle, which is the mystic cement of our
   fellowship, remain with us and bless us. Amen!

Response: So mote it be.

## DECLARATION & ATTENDING THE ALTAR

IM: (_Returning to station, while other officers remain on
  the level._) In the name of God and our Three Ancient
  Grand Masters, I declare {{blank 6em}} Council |
  No. {{blank 2em}}, Cryptic Masons closed on the Select Master
  Degree in form. (_I._M. recovers._) Companion
  Conductor of the Council, close the Great Lights.

Note: C._C. advances to altar, squaring corners, removes
   the Square and Compasses, closes the Volume of the
   Sacred Law, and returns before station without saluting.

## INFORMING THE SENTINEL

IM: Companion Captain of the Guard, inform the Sentinel.
CG: Companion Steward, inform the Sentinel.
%PAGE
Note: Without saluting, the Steward goes to the door
   and gives ●●● ●●● ●●● to call up the Sentinel. |
   The Sentinel acknowledges by returning the same |
   ●●● ●●● ●●●.

Stew: (_Opens door._) Companion Sentinel, this Council is
   closed on the Select Master Degree in form. (_Door may
   remain open at this point. Steward returns to station
   and faces C._G. without saluting_) Companion Captain
   of the Guard, your order has been obeyed.
CG: (_Without saluting._) Illustrious Master, your order has
   been obeyed.
IM: ●

